description: Will she be able to reign the phone dragons?
maintext: Women walk past an advertising poster to promote the HBO American fantasy drama television series Game of Thrones outside the International Game of Thrones exhibition in Stockholm on March 11, 2015. According to the television network HBO the fifth season of the fantasy drama television series Game of Thrones will start on April 12, 2015.
